Body:
And when he turneth away (from thee) his effort in the land is to
			make mischief therein and to destroy the crops and the cattle;
			and Allah loveth not mischief.

O ye who believe! Come, all of you, into submission (unto Him);
			and follow not the footsteps of the devil. Lo! he is an open
			enemy for you.

These are the portents of Allah which We recite unto thee
			(Muhammad) with truth, and Lo! thou art of the number of (Our)
			messengers;
